Bat Wif Dog

Hey, a little bit about me, my name is Axl and i'm here looking for a group of woofing dogs that used to live on my block but have since ran off owing me coin.

You may have heard of them, they go by the names:

Bonk, Floki, Wif, Shiba and Doge.

They can run but they can't hide!

Now that im fully equipped with my bat and bandana im ready to travel to every city in the world to hunt down these memeing dogs.

But before we take over the scene, we're going to need a few recruits, a few badass bruisers would do just fine!

And once we start getting some momentum, it wont be long until we catch up with that woofing dogwifhat and knock that silly hat off his head!

Sorry for my messy handwriting, you will have to excuse me, afterall, I'm just a dog.
